ABUJA – President Muhammadu Buhari has approved the redeployment of Mrs. Didi Walson-Jack, Permanent Secretary, Staff Welfare Office in the Office of the Head of the Civil Service of the Federation to the Ministry of Niger Delta Affairs. The circular conveying the redeployment was signed by the Head of the Civil Service of the Federation, Mrs. Winifred Oyo-Ita. A statement by the Director of Communications, OHCSF, Mrs. Olawunmi Ogunmosunle, said the handing/taking over processes should be completed on or before Friday, August 2, 2019.